係好穩陣</blockquote><br />\n我用百度地度OK喎<br />\n又教我邊到要靠左或右渣<br />\n前面燈位係直去左轉右轉都講得好清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n等我睇下百度先"},{"pid":"92002bfeb2b2e6fc487a74d48f54127e7870d566","tid":227150,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:07:52.000Z","msg":"暫時用過  高德準過Google map <br />\n申 iPhone"},{"pid":"8462af437baa78ceaa98de9a32338dbfa9eaa4a8","tid":227150,"uid":24966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:18:22.000Z","msg":"連登做乜事<br />\n一大堆大陸仔係到用埋d支那satnav"},{"pid":"244aa516ee6286738b9c8e0ab29c25ac25d5e96d","tid":227150,"uid":60840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暫時用過  高德準過Google map <br />\n申 iPhone</blockquote><br />\n之前跟Google map諗住由大坑道落紅隧過海，佢叫我上告士打道天橋落告士打道<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落到去先知根本冇得cut入去排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632f02573c8d168f997082986710341b6be073af","tid":227150,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:28:42.000Z","msg":"咁呢d不嬲用來參考啦<br />\n咁暫時無乜邊個app正喎<br />\n你要100%根本無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要100%準就收你錢啦<br />\n免費 + 準確度無8成都7成<br />\n我覺得無得輸"},{"pid":"17d48eae1752024a5a202a9a3cbcc40258fc4275","tid":227150,"uid":4032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:31:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n我用百度地度OK喎<br />\n又教我邊到要靠左或右渣<br />\n前面燈位係直去左轉右轉都講得好清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係百度真係全殘體，又得普通話。<br />\n<br />\n高德起碼地圖啲字係正體，同叫做有廣東話。<br />\n<br />\n重點係語音導航幾乎唔使睇個 screen，齋聽聲都大約可以跟到。例如要跟邊條線先轉到右，導航都會講埋。Google map 就要望 screen。<br />\n<br />\n地點就真係唔係好齊。如果去一個唔識嘅地方驚中伏，唯有先開 Google map cross check。"},{"pid":"6ac000596e88fb8743c5db9f33664ccb048f95dc","tid":227150,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登做乜事<br />\n一大堆大陸仔係到用埋d支那satnav</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那app真係唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有本地製作"},{"pid":"6510fe62cb334d422bb5c5bad36ee9a0bc389187","tid":227150,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"高德一定好過google"},{"pid":"7ff15dcffe9e48d2ebeb36c1e0edcb3beae12d20","tid":227150,"uid":57800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:22:48.000Z","msg":"支那app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家用緊google map, 就算佢收皮都好, 總之一日有其他選擇我都唔會裝支那野用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d118dde25edcdc77c2043c155f5ba6d0cfbe341a","tid":227150,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家用緊google map, 就算佢收皮都好, 總之一日有其他選擇我都唔會裝支那野用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n彌敦道瘋狂u turn <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad2258d2d00a49c2379093813f39dc3d9882fb2","tid":227150,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fd3e884eb11606f3735c927ec52980e12729b63","tid":227150,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"同google比佢好好多啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caee44e5981788eaeac2b8adf1062a83c9b07dd2","tid":227150,"uid":665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:32:12.000Z","msg":"投高德一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}